64 REM ============================================================
65 REM Player + trail + minimap state. RIBWAL is the 1-unit grid of P1 ribbon cells (2-player uses it for AI avoidance).
66 REM ============================================================
67 PX=CELL*8 : PZ=CELL*8
68 PYAW=0 : CUBEYAW=0 : MOVING=0 : CAMMODE=0 : AUTORUN=0 : JUMPY=0 : JUMPV=0 : LIGHTON=1 : WIREMODE=0 : CAMPITCH=0 : BLOOMON=1 : FPSON=1 : TURNMODE=0 : TURNTGT=0 : AAON=1 : SPDCUR=SPEED
69 DIM TRLID(2000)
